title: Proudmoon Tomb
story: The tomb is situated on a lonely island. Lately a fearsome basilisk has made its home here. The tomb is a place of growth of a valuable specie of fungi.

notes.text: A lavishly decorated ironclad gate on the southern wall of the small room.
A giant pile of rubble hides a robe.
A confident dwarf, sitting in a corner.
A corpse of a wizard, a blood-stained glaive and rations close by.
